## Technical Requirements

### Video Features
- All videos use privacy-enhanced mode (`youtube-nocookie.com`)
- `rel=0` parameter limits recommendations to same channel only
- JavaScript automatically stops videos when they end (prevents related videos)
- Timestamp buttons automatically seek and play
- Responsive 16:9 aspect ratio containers

### Image Features
- Lazy loading for performance
- Semantic HTML5 structure
- Accessible alt text required
- Caption and credit always included

