## Best Practices

1. **Always provide context** - Add brief description before video/image
2. **Use descriptive titles** - Video titles should be clear and informative
3. **Add timestamps for long videos** - Help students navigate content
4. **Include captions** - Images need descriptive captions explaining relevance
5. **Maintain consistency** - Follow the established patterns
6. **Test locally** - Verify videos/images work after adding
7. **Accessibility first** - Always include alt text and descriptive titles

